{"tid":2142234,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"廣島原爆75週年 日本重申不簽禁止核武器條約","createTime":"2020-08-06T09:22:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-07T09:29:33.000Z","uid":184679,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"25f840ca6ec5c5845902b7068f951d7b259cfb1d","tid":2142234,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T09:22:49.000Z","msg":"日本廣島市今天迎接原子彈爆炸75週年，市長松井一實再度公開呼籲日本政府簽署並批准禁止核武器條約，不過，日本首相安倍晉三與相關代表會面時，再度表達否定態度。<br />\n<br />\n適逢廣島原爆75週年，今天上午在廣島市和平公園舉行的和平紀念儀式上，共有受難者代表、罹難者家屬代表、安倍晉三，及來自全球83個國家的代表參與。<br />\n<br />\n聯合國曾在2017年通過禁止核武器條約（Treatyon the Prohibition of Nuclear Weapons），將在簽署國中有50國批准後生效，目前已知截至今年7月止，已有40個國家批准；但唯一被原子彈轟炸的日本卻沒有參與。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/6809/4760999\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F6809%2F4760999&d=il%2BrReVPph3FBkDtfLAFOi%2B7EDXmwg1SXj7S5MqlT1o%3D&h=c844a691\" target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/6809/4760999</a>"},{"pid":"ac2a90e43644e7a2eba52439e2518a7e1e186999","tid":2142234,"uid":8014,"like":1,"dislike":11,"score":-10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T09:25:48.000Z","msg":"日本想還番粒核彈比美國？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c3fc3c602f3095bca6497ae2a18c44badc021a0","tid":2142234,"uid":256019,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"ac2a90e43644e7a2eba52439e2518a7e1e186999","tid":2142234,"uid":8014,"like":1,"dislike":11,"score":-10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T09:25:48.000Z","msg":"日本想還番粒核彈比美國？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T09:28:17.000Z","msg":"未必！似乎係提防支那、俄佬、北韓多於美國.."},{"pid":"a37637b372b9d02e7bbd0071865db69f7376f580","tid":2142234,"uid":40267,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T09:28:49.000Z","msg":"叫哥9個擁核國嘔翻啲核彈出嚟先講啦"},{"pid":"22d47a3f6e3777b8a7ddb2ead7faf832f8414611","tid":2142234,"uid":78873,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T09:29:45.00